When doing a filter that lists a few sub-tasks, the sub-task summary is displayed as follows:

{code}
<Parent Issue Key> / <Sub-Task Summary>
i.e. "ISSUE-123 / My sub-task's summary"
{code}

Is it possible to instead show the parent issue's summary followed by its sub-task's summary?

{code}
i.e. "My parent issue's summary / My sub-task's summary"
{code}

This would be very similar to how the breadcrumbs are displayed when looking at a sub-task, except the parent issue key would not be displayed.

